# MTG EDH Deck Manager вЂ” Project Context & Architecture

> This file serves as a quick-reference skill for understanding the MTGDeckManager codebase.
> Generated: 2026-05-05 | Repo: https://github.com/GavinHungaski/MTGDeckManager

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Frontend | React 19, React Router 7, Vite 7, Axios |
| Backend | Node.js, Express 5, ES Modules (`"type": "module"`) |
| Database | PostgreSQL 14+ on AWS RDS |
| External API | Scryfall (card data) |
| Deployment | Backend: AWS Elastic Beanstalk; DB: AWS RDS; Frontend: Not yet deployed |

