## Database Schema

### users
- `id` UUID PK (uuid-ossp)
- `username` VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL
- `email` TEXT вЂ” **encrypted** (AES-256-GCM)
- `email_hash` VARCHAR(64) UNIQUE вЂ” SHA256 for login lookups
- `password_hash` TEXT вЂ” bcrypt
- `created_at`, `updated_at` TIMESTAMPZ

### decks
- `id` UUID PK
- `user_id` UUID FK в†’ users ON DELETE CASCADE
- `name` VARCHAR(200)
- `format` VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'Commander'
- `commander_card_id` VARCHAR(100) вЂ” Scryfall ID
- `is_public` BOOLEAN DEFAULT false

### cards
- `id` VARCHAR(100) PK вЂ” **Scryfall card ID**
- `name`, `mana_cost`, `cmc`, `card_type`, `oracle_text`, `power`, `toughness`, `loyalty`, `artist`, `rarity`
- `prices` JSONB, `image_uris` JSONB, `legalities` JSONB, `types` JSONB
- `color_identity` TEXT[], `keywords` TEXT[]
- `edhrec_rank` INTEGER, `back_image` TEXT

### deck_cards (junction)
- `id` UUID PK
- `deck_id` UUID FK в†’ decks ON DELETE CASCADE
- `card_id` VARCHAR(100) FK в†’ cards
- `quantity` INTEGER DEFAULT 1
- `is_commander` BOOLEAN DEFAULT false
- `is_sideboard` BOOLEAN DEFAULT false
- `notes` TEXT
- UNIQUE(deck_id, card_id)

---

## Data Pathways

### 1. Authentication
```
Login/Register
  в†’ client/services/api.js в†’ authAPI.login/register
    в†’ POST /api/auth/login or /register
      в†’ auth.routes.js в†’ auth.service.js
        в†’ bcrypt compare/hash
        в†’ JWT sign (7d expiry)
        в†’ Pool query (users table)
    в†ђ { token, user }
  в†ђ localStorage.setItem('token')
  в†ђ AuthContext updates (token, user, isAuthenticated)
```

### 2. Deck List
```
Decks Page
  в†’ deckAPI.getAll()
    в†’ GET /api/decks
      в†’ authenticate middleware в†’ deck.routes.js
        в†’ deck.service.js::getAllDecks(userId)
          в†’ SQL: JOIN decks + deck_cards (is_commander) + cards
          в†’ JSON_AGG commanders + SUM(card_count)
    в†ђ [{ id, name, commanders[], count }]
```

### 3. Deck Detail / Editor
```
DeckDetail
  в†’ deckAPI.getById(deckId)
    в†’ GET /api/decks/:id
      в†’ deck.service.js::getDeckById(id, userId)
        в†’ SQL: LEFT JOIN decks + deck_cards + cards
        в†’ Returns all card fields (image_uris, prices, types, etc.)
  в†ђ { id, name, commanders[], cards[] }

Add Card
  в†’ cardAPI.add(deckId, cardData)
    в†’ POST /api/cards/decks/:deckId/card
      в†’ card.service.js::addCardToDeck()
        в†’ verifyDeckOwnership()
        в†’ UPSERT cards table (by Scryfall id)
        в†’ INSERT or UPDATE deck_cards (increment quantity)

Remove Card
  в†’ cardAPI.remove(deckId, cardId)
    в†’ DELETE /api/cards/decks/:deckId/card/:cardId
      в†’ Decrement quantity or DELETE from deck_cards

Toggle Commander
  в†’ cardAPI.toggleCommander(deckId, cardId)
    в†’ PATCH /api/cards/decks/:deckId/card/:cardId/commander
      в†’ Flip is_commander boolean
```

### 4. Search (Scryfall вЂ” No Backend)
```
Search Page / CardSearch component
  в†’ Direct fetch to https://api.scryfall.com/cards/search?q=...
  в†’ Query built from: text, colors, CMC, types, rarities, sort
  в†’ Always includes: f:commander -is:digital
  в†’ Results processed: split type_line into supertypes/types/subtypes
  в†’ Can add to decks via DeckTray в†’ backend card API
```

### 5. Playtest
```
Playtest Page
  в†’ Raw fetch to /api/decks/:deckId (not api.js!)
  в†’ formatCard() extracts image_uris.normal
  в†’ expandAndShuffle() в†’ library, deck, commandZone
  в†’ useReducer (playtestReducer) manages:
     - Zones: deck, hand, graveyard, exile, commandZone, battlefield
     - Players: life(40), poison, experience, energy, rad, commanderDamage
     - UI: contextMenu, tokenCreatorOpen, deckSearcherOpen, etc.
  в†’ React Konva canvas for battlefield
```

